<H3>Target Markets</H3>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><FONT face=Arial><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">Our target markets are ISP's Communities and small businesses in <?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags" /><st1:country-region><st1:place>Canada where </st1:place></st1:country-region>the&nbsp;current form of internet connectivity is the telephone line or expensive satellite systems.<?XML:NAMESPACE PREFIX = O /><O:P></O:P></SPAN></FONT></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><FONT face=Arial><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-weight: bold"></SPAN></FONT>&nbsp;</P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><FONT face=Arial><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">Existing and start-up ISP's whose current <st1:PersonName>mark</st1:PersonName>et demands higher internet access speeds where the ISP does not have the expertise in house to design and implement such a solution. Where an affordable, quick deployment, last mile solution is needed. </SPAN></FONT></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><FONT face=Arial><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-weight: bold"></SPAN></FONT>&nbsp;</P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><FONT face=Arial><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-weight: bold"><A href="http://www.broadband.gc.ca/maps/maps_e.asp" target=_blank>Canadian communities </A>is our biggest market. Industry </SPAN><st1:country-region><st1:place><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">Canada</SPAN></st1:place></st1:country-region><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">'s Broadband for Rural and Northern Development Pilot Program has attracted over 220 community applicants who require funding for their local internet access requirements. This Industry Canada broadband initiative is part of the Government of Canada's commitment to ensuring broadband access for all Canadian communities by 2005. Over $100M are allocated to community sponsored groups. Many of these groups have no expertise in implementing such a solution.<?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-weight: bold"><o:p><FONT face=Arial>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-weight: bold"><FONT face=Arial>We are targeting small businesses&nbsp;such as marinas, car dealerships, hotels, schools etc. that require ōHot Spotsö. ōHot Spotsö are becoming more popular as hand held devices become useful in providing mobile access to internet data.</FONT></SPAN><o:p></o:p></P>
